   "source": [
    "# 工资计算系统 - Android APK构建器\n",
    "\n",
    "这个Colab笔记本将帮助您轻松构建工资计算系统的Android APK文件。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 步骤1: 安装必要的依赖"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "!pip install --upgrade buildozer"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步骤2: 设置项目目录"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 创建项目目录\n",
    "!mkdir -p /content/salary_app\n",
    "%cd /content/salary_app"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步骤3: 上传项目文件\n",
    "\n",
    "点击下方的文件上传按钮，上传以下文件：\n",
    "- salary_calculator.py\n",
    "- main.py\n",
    "- android_tkinter_fix.py\n",
    "- common_utils.py\n",
    "- buildozer.spec\n",
    "- 以及其他必要的文件和数据库"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from google.colab import files\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建一个用于上传的按钮\n",
    "uploaded = files.upload()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 显示上传的文件列表\n",
    "print("\n上传的文件：")\n",
    "for fn in uploaded.keys():\n",
    "  print('文件名: "%s" 大小: %d bytes' % (fn, len(uploaded[fn])))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步骤4: 初始化Buildozer环境"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 如果没有buildozer.spec文件，则初始化一个\n",
    "!if [ ! -f buildozer.spec ]; then buildozer init; fi\n",
    "\n",
    "# 检查当前目录中的文件\n",
    "!ls -la"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步骤5: 配置构建环境\n",
    "\n",
    "执行以下命令来安装构建Android APK所需的系统依赖。这可能需要一些时间。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 安装构建依赖\n",
    "!apt-get update -y\n",
    "!apt-get install -y git zip unzip openjdk-17-jdk python3-pip autoconf libtool pkg-config zlib1g-dev libncurses5-dev libncursesw5-dev libtinfo5 cmake libffi-dev libssl-dev"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步骤6: 开始构建APK\n",
    "\n",
    "这是关键步骤，将开始构建Android APK文件。请注意，这可能需要1-2小时，具体取决于网络速度和资源可用性。\n",
    "\n",
    "请耐心等待，不要关闭此页面。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 开始构建APK（调试版本）\n",
    "!buildozer -v android debug"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 步骤7: 下载生成的APK文件\n",
    "\n",
    "如果构建成功，您可以下载生成的APK文件到您的电脑上。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 查看生成的APK文件\n",
    "!ls -la bin/\n",
    "\n",
    "# 下载APK文件到本地\n",
    "from google.colab import files\n",
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "# 查找bin目录中的APK文件\n",
    "apk_files = [f for f in os.listdir('bin') if f.endswith('.apk')]\n",
    "\n",
    "if apk_files:\n",
    "    latest_apk = max(apk_files, key=lambda x: os.path.getctime(os.path.join('bin', x)))\n",
    "    print(f"准备下载最新的APK文件: {latest_apk}")\n",
    "    files.download(os.path.join('bin', latest_apk))\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print("没有找到生成的APK文件，请检查构建日志以获取详细信息。")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 构建问题排查\n",
    "\n",
    "如果构建失败，可以查看详细的日志信息来排查问题。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 查看最近的构建日志\n",
    "!tail -n 100 buildozer.log"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 常见问题与解决方案\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. 构建超时\n",
    "**解决方法**: 增加Buildozer的超时设置，可以编辑buildozer.spec文件。\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. 依赖下载失败\n",
    "**解决方法**: 检查网络连接，重新运行构建命令。\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. Tkinter相关错误\n",
    "**解决方法**: 确保已包含android_tkinter_fix.py文件，它包含了必要的兼容性修复。\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4. 内存不足\n",
    "**解决方法**: 在Colab中，尝试使用更高配置的运行时（通过"运行时" > "更改运行时类型" > "硬件加速器"选择GPU）。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 扩展选项: 构建发布版本\n",
    "\n",
    "如果您需要构建用于发布的APK文件（非调试版本），可以使用以下命令。请注意，这需要配置签名密钥。" 
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
